{"word":"Capernaum","slug":"capernaum","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Capernaum</b> A city on the shore of the Sea of Galilee.<br/> Jesus chose, as the place of his abode<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=13'>Mat 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=31'>Luk 4:31</a><br/> Miracles of Jesus performed at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=26'>Mat 9:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=27'>Mat 17:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=45'>Mar 1:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2'>Mar 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=6'>Mar 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=10'>Luk 7:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=53'>Joh 4:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=25'>Joh 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=59'>Joh 6:59</a><br/> His prophecy against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=23'>Mat 11:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=15'>Luk 10:15</a>"}]}